OL,3,CCourt hears man caused wife to take
OL,4,Cown life by violently controlling her
OL,6,FA man controlled his wife through
OL,7,F"physical and sexual violence",
OL,8,Fleading to her taking her own life
OL,9,Fbecause she could not escape him, a
OL,10,Fcourt has heard.
OL,12,FChristopher Trybus, from Swindon,
OL,13,FWiltshire, is accused of the
OL,14,Fmanslaughter of Tarryn Baird, who died
OL,15,Fof hanging in November 2017 at the age
OL,16,Fof 34.
OL,18,FThe 43-year-old also faces charges at
OL,19,FWinchester Crown Court of controlling
OL,20,Fand coercive behaviour and two charges
OL,21,Fof rape.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@^O]
