OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772110990
OL,3,CCourt hears man caused wife to take
OL,4,Cown life by violently controlling her
OL,6,FThe coercive control charge alleges
OL,7,Fthat Trybus controlled Ms Baird
OL,8,Fthrough using and threatening violence
OL,9,Ftowards her, sexually assaulting her,
OL,10,Fmonitoring her whereabouts, limiting
OL,11,Faccess to finance, threatening to
OL,12,Freveal private information to her
OL,13,Ffamily and isolating her from her
OL,14,Ffamily.
OL,16,FTom Little KC, prosecuting told the
OL,17,Fjury that Trybus carried out
OL,18,F"extensive and escalating controlling,
OL,19,Fcoercive and manipulative behaviour
OL,20,Fincluding sexual violence of two rapes
OL,21,Fand other sexual assaults".
OL,26,@zD@AOU}D@ZO]
