OL,3,CCourt hears man caused wife to take
OL,4,Cown life by violently controlling her
OL,6,FHe continued: "It took place over a
OL,7,Fsustained period of time behind closed
OL,8,Fdoors and all of it during the course
OL,9,Fof a marriage.
OL,11,F"It led ultimately in November 2017 to
OL,12,Fa woman in just her thirties and whose
OL,13,Fname is Tarryn Baird taking her own
OL,14,Flife by hanging.
OL,16,F"She was the defendant's wife and the
OL,17,Fprosecution say that the defendant is
OL,18,Flegally responsible for her death."
OL,26,@nD@OOUsD@AOUxD@AOUzD@cO]
