OL,3,CCourt hears man caused wife to take
OL,4,Cown life by violently controlling her
OL,6,FMr Little explained that Trybus
OL,7,Fcontrolled "many aspects of their
OL,8,Frelationship" even from abroad using
OL,9,Fthe "threat and fear of physical and
OL,10,Fsexual violence" leading to a
OL,11,Fdeterioration in her "already weakened
OL,12,Fmental state and a cause of her
OL,13,Fdeciding that she should take her own
OL,14,Flife".
OL,16,FHe added: "She did so in their own
OL,17,Fhome.
OL,19,F"She had not managed to escape from
OL,20,Fhim, despite seriously considering
OL,21,Fdoing so on a number of occasions.
OL,26,@oD@LOUpD@MO]qD@EOUrD@PO]sD@VOUvD@EO]xD@
OL,26,AKOU{D@AOU
