OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772110990
OL,3,CCourt hears man caused wife to take
OL,4,Cown life by violently controlling her
OL,6,F"However, we say that constricted by
OL,7,Fhis control she could never go through
OL,8,Fwith leaving him, no doubt fearing the
OL,9,Fconsequences if she would try to do
OL,10,Fso, and instead she stopped his
OL,11,Fcontrol over her in the only way she
OL,12,Ffelt she could by taking her own life."
OL,14,FMr Little said that Ms Baird, who
OL,15,Fworked at an opticians, left a note
OL,16,Fwhich said: "To my family, I am so
OL,17,Fsorry but I just couldn't take it any
OL,18,Fmore.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@gO]xD@MOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
