CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772110990
OL,3,CCourt hears man caused wife to take
OL,4,Cown life by violently controlling her
OL,6,F"I know you may not understand this
OL,7,Fbut I just can't explain the dark
OL,8,Fcloud that is over me.
OL,10,F"Please don't let this break you but
OL,11,Fknow I am now free. Nothing any of you
OL,12,Fcould have done could have changed
OL,13,Fthis, please just know that.
OL,15,F"I love you and please forgive me."
OL,17,FMr Little said the couple, both from
OL,18,FSouth Africa, moved to the UK in 2007
OL,19,Fand married in 2009.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUwD@AOUwD@cO]
